Suggestions 5

1.Increase innovation : For farmers to increase both yield and profits they should leverage data and innovation to improve productivity. Technology is changing Agriculture by introducing soil sensors, GPS-equipped tractors and weather tracking giving farmers opportunities to maximize resources. As farmers access to real-time data they gain the information they need to plan, Prepare increasing Productivity and profitability.

2. Poor inventory of all farming equipment, farming building, inputs, furniture etc., has decreased farm productivity and profitability. All farmers should perform Proper inventory which gives them an idea of the value and the current state of the items. Farmers should ensure that the inventory is done at the beginning and the end of the production year.
